flegt yeder eyner mitnemen

00:11:44.099 --> 00:11:45.977
a shisele

00:11:45.977 --> 00:11:49.707
a kesele, a vos nit iz, az me zol a-

00:11:49.707 --> 00:11:53.923
arayn-, kenen arayngisn a teler

