vi alt?

00:12:14.651 --> 00:12:18.259
yo, fir un tsvantsik, finf un tsvantsik.

00:12:18.259 --> 00:12:23.908
gedenk shoyn aleyn nit.

00:12:23.908 --> 00:12:27.327
un, ye, az nokh

00:12:27.327 --> 00:12:30.840
a nomen hot men gegebn di daytshn "a yale geyt."

00:12:30.840 --> 00:12:34.502
az me flegt a mol arbetn, az me zet az zey geyen, flegt men zogn azoy

00:12:34.502 --> 00:12:36.934
"⟨der⟩ yale geyt, der yale geyt."

00:12:36.934 --> 00:12:39.353
 m'hot a nomen gegebn di

00:12:39.353 --> 00:12:42.894
di daytshn, di, di UNK a yale, a hekherer.

00:12:42.894 --> 00:12:46.069
ye, ⟨me flegt⟩ zogn az a yale geyt.

00:12:46.069 --> 00:12:49.704
m'hot gearbet. nokh dem

00:12:49.704 --> 00:12:52.068
hob ikh opgearbet oyfn erodrom

00:12:52.068 --> 00:12:56.636
un dos iz shoyn geven der

00:12:56.636 --> 00:13:04.082
in, in eyn un f- tsvey un fertsikstn yor. in tsvey un fertsikstn yor iz geven zeyer a kalter vinter.

00:13:04.082 --> 00:13:08.487
a frostike. me flegt darfn geyn oyfn erodrom.

00:13:08.487 --> 00:13:10.838
tsu Slabodke

00:13:10.838 --> 00:13:14.797
flegt men darfn fun Slabodke aribergeyn

00:13:14.797 --> 00:13:18.095
biz oyfn erodrom; dos iz

00:13:18.095 --> 00:13:20.135
aribergeyn tsvey brikn

00:13:20.135 --> 00:13:23.473
un aribergeyn UNK oyf a barg

00:13:23.473 --> 00:13:25.432
kilometers vayt

00:13:25.432 --> 00:13:28.243
flegt men darfn geyn biz vanet

00:13:28.243 --> 00:13:29.175
men hot

00:13:29.175 --> 00:13:33.621
undz, flegt men kumen tsu do, oyfn erodrom.

00:13:33.621 --> 00:13:38.121
az ⟨der⟩ flegt geyn nokh mir, flegt geyn fun di ershte flegt men geyn.

00:13:38.121 --> 00:13:41.878
ven ⟨ikh bin⟩ a mol flegt pasirn az me geyt fun di letste

00:13:41.878 --> 00:13:45.351
flegt men di gantse veg darfn loyfn.

00:13:45.351 --> 00:13:48.823
"LAUFEN, LAUFEN, SCHNELLER, SCHNELLER, LAUFEN."

00:13:48.823 --> 00:13:52.079
un mir darfn loyfn alts di gantse veg loyfn

00:13:52.079 --> 00:13:57.228
biz vanet me flegt kumen d- un dos iz geven oyf a barg in der heykh aroyftsugeyn.

00:13:57.228 --> 00:13:59.093
flegt aroyfgeyn dem barg

00:13:59.093 --> 00:14:03.390
un biz vanet me flegt kumen dortn oyfn erodrom flegt men darfn geyn

00:14:03.390 --> 00:14:05.336
kilometers tsu fus.

00:14:05.336 --> 00:14:09.200
me-, host gemeynt a mol antlofn?

00:14:09.200 --> 00:14:11.011
host gevolt antlofn?

00:14:11.011 --> 00:14:14.335
avu loyfn? vu ⟨zol men⟩ loyfn?

00:14:14.335 --> 00:14:16.024
shoyn nito vu tsu loyfn.

00:14:16.024 --> 00:14:18.022
UNK nemen dokh nit tsu

00:14:18.022 --> 00:14:20.903
di litviner hobn aleyn moyre gehat.

00:14:20.903 --> 00:14:24.187
vayl m'hot gezogt azoy, az di litviner

00:14:24.187 --> 00:14:26.388
ver es vet oyshitn a yidn

00:14:26.388 --> 00:14:28.078
shist men zey oyset.

00:14:28.078 --> 00:14:30.105
hobn zey aleyn moyre gehat.

00:14:30.105 --> 00:14:31.591
geven in tsaytung

00:14:31.591 --> 00:14:34.970
in geto az me darf opgebn di gold.

00:14:34.970 --> 00:14:37.672
ye ale darfn vos me hot gold

00:14:37.672 --> 00:14:40.686
tsirung, brilyantn

00:14:40.686 --> 00:14:42.997
alts darf vern opgegebn.

00:14:42.997 --> 00:14:44.942
ver es vet nit opgebn

00:14:44.942 --> 00:14:48.266
vet men geyn in di shtiber, un m'vet kontrolirn.

00:14:48.266 --> 00:14:53.009
oyb m'vet gefinen az m'hot nit opgegebn di, di, di gel- di gold

00:14:53.009 --> 00:14:56.239
vert oysgeshosn der gantser kvartal.

00:14:56.239 --> 00:14:58.009
alemen vet men oysshisn.

00:14:58.009 --> 00:15:00.374
oyb me vet bagrobn vu nit vu

00:15:00.374 --> 00:15:04.522
un m'vet bahaltn, vet men geyn mit groyse

00:15:04.522 --> 00:15:07.373
azelkhene, mit sh- shtekhn in di erd

00:15:07.373 --> 00:15:11.414
un m'vet zukhn oyber m'hot nit bahaltn vu gold.

00:15:11.414 --> 00:15:13.414
oyber m'vet gefunen, gefinen

00:15:13.414 --> 00:15:16.049
vu nit vu bay vemen bahaltene gold

00:15:16.049 --> 00:15:19.968
vern ale, ale vern dershosn.

00:15:20.065 --> 00:15:21.894
du host gehat epes?

00:15:20.223 --> 00:15:20.947
un az

00:15:22.318 --> 00:15:25.007
ikh hob keyn zakh nit gehat; mayn shvester hot avekgegebn

00:15:25.007 --> 00:15:28.683
UNK gegebn ⟨oyf ir⟩ dem, dem, ringele vos, UNK

00:15:28.683 --> 00:15:29.947
fun,

00:15:29.426 --> 00:15:30.224
khasene.

00:15:30.224 --> 00:15:33.102
ye. avekgegebn.

00:15:33.102 --> 00:15:38.183
ale hobn avekgegebn. ale nit- m'hot moyre ge-. far shrek un far moyre.

00:15:38.183 --> 00:15:41.101
hot men getrogn az m'hot gevorfn dortn

00:15:41.101 --> 00:15:43.426
in a, in a, in a top aza

00:15:43.426 --> 00:15:46.223
un m'hot gevorfn di gold mit di brilyantn, mit, mit

00:15:46.223 --> 00:15:54.290
di keytelekh mit vos, vos eyner hot farmogt, alts hot men avekgegebn di, di daytshn.

00:15:54.290 --> 00:15:56.817
vos iz geven vayter?

00:15:56.817 --> 00:15:57.453
?

00:15:57.453 --> 00:16:00.249
vos iz geven vayter?

00:16:00.249 --> 00:16:03.533
nu, hot men gearbet.

00:16:03.533 --> 00:16:07.722
az dernokh hob ikh gearbet

00:16:07.722 --> 00:16:11.776
shoyn UNK? az dernokh hob ikh gearbet

00:16:11.776 --> 00:16:14.127
geven a brigade

00:16:14.127 --> 00:16:19.018
di UNK. dos iz geven oykh oyf a barg

00:16:19.018 --> 00:16:22.667
un, hot men genumen eyntslne froyen

00:16:22.667 --> 00:16:25.383
bin ikh oykh arayngefaln dortn.

00:16:25.383 --> 00:16:28.302
dortn iz geven, dos iz geven

00:16:28.302 --> 00:16:30.613
oyf land virtshaft arbet.

00:16:30.613 --> 00:16:33.802
tsu arbetn di felder.

00:16:33.802 --> 00:16:35.694
dortn iz geven a barak.

00:16:35.694 --> 00:16:38.923
in barak iz geven dray-etazhne betlekh.

00:16:38.923 --> 00:16:41.828
un mir geven froyen, nor froyen.

00:16:41.828 --> 00:16:47.463
un dortn zaynen mir geshlofn a gantse vokh; oyf shabes flegt men undz firn in geto.

00:16:47.463 --> 00:16:51.085
un m'hot gearbet dortn oyf di felder.

00:16:51.085 --> 00:16:55.869
vos m'hot gedarft ale arbet vos me darf oyf a UNK felder.

00:16:55.869 --> 00:16:59.800
nor eyn tsayt a bisl hob ikh gearbet bay di shnayderay.

00:16:59.800 --> 00:17:04.057
bay di, ⟨der⟩ vos hot gehaltn, der daytsh

00:17:04.057 --> 00:17:06.719
di, di, di firme

00:17:06.719 --> 00:17:10.652
di, hot er, far di vayber

00:17:10.652 --> 00:17:14.540
⟨hob ikh⟩ geneyt.

00:17:14.540 --> 00:17:16.929
dos iz geven tsvey un fertsik yor.

00:17:16.770 --> 00:17:18.286
ye, dos iz shoyn geven in

00:17:18.286 --> 00:17:20.540
dos iz shoyn geven in dray un fertsikstn yor

00:17:21.229 --> 00:17:22.756
in dray un fertsikstn yor.

00:17:22.756 --> 00:17:25.539
un di shvester mit di kinder ale tsuzamen?

00:17:25.539 --> 00:17:28.144
ale zaynen mir gelebt tsuzamen, yo un der bruder

00:17:27.120 --> 00:17:28.255
un di shvoger?

00:17:28.255 --> 00:17:30.092
un der bruder, der bruder velkher

00:17:29.458 --> 00:17:30.269
Yosef.

00:17:30.269 --> 00:17:31.836
Yosef, ye, er iz geven.

00:17:31.836 --> 00:17:34.877
nor der bruder az dernokh m'hot genumen

00:17:34.877 --> 00:17:37.404
in, in velkhn yor?

00:17:37.404 --> 00:17:39.377
in tsvey un fertsikstn yor, dakht zikh

00:17:39.377 --> 00:17:41.242
hot men genumen oyf Kedan.

00:17:41.242 --> 00:17:42.592
Kedan, dos iz

00:17:42.592 --> 00:17:45.241
oykhet in Lite.

00:17:45.241 --> 00:17:50.200
hot men genumen a brigade. iz er avek oyf Kedan.

00:17:50.200 --> 00:17:54.092
hot er shoyn nit gelebt mit undz in, in Slabodke.

00:17:54.092 --> 00:17:56.214
nor er iz geven in Kedan.

00:17:56.214 --> 00:17:58.579
nor ts- fun tsayt tsu tsayt a mol

00:17:58.579 --> 00:18:01.769
flegt men zey oplozn, un brengen tsu firn, flegt er kumen tsu

00:18:01.769 --> 00:18:05.188
forn, tsu undz in geto.

00:18:05.188 --> 00:18:09.215
ober er iz geven shoyn nit mit undz tsuzamen.

00:18:09.215 --> 00:18:11.094
tsuzamen bin ikh geven mit

00:18:11.094 --> 00:18:13.458
di gantse yorn mit mayn shvester

00:18:13.458 --> 00:18:18.228
un mit di, mit di ki- mitn shvoger mit di kinder.

00:18:18.228 --> 00:18:20.431
mit vos hot gearbet der shvoger?

00:18:20.431 --> 00:18:24.512
oykh a shnayder. hot er gen- er iz er in Kovne

00:18:24.512 --> 00:18:26.863
flegt men im firn in Kovne

00:18:26.863 --> 00:18:29.485
un, er hot dortn geneyt

00:18:29.485 --> 00:18:33.174
far di, far di daytshn.

00:18:33.174 --> 00:18:36.795
ye. vos iz geven vayter?

00:18:36.795 --> 00:18:39.416
dos iz geven

00:18:39.416 --> 00:18:44.943
in, in dray un fertsikstn yor bin ikh shoyn geven oyf di UNK arbet

00:18:44.943 --> 00:18:47.389
az s'iz farmakht, dos iz geven, f-

00:18:47.389 --> 00:18:50.578
onfang, onfang zumer.

00:18:50.578 --> 00:18:53.295
az s'iz farmakht di UNK

00:18:53.295 --> 00:18:55.956
bin ikh, iz geven

00:18:55.956 --> 00:18:59.618
a brigade, MAREVYANKA hot dos geheysn.

00:18:59.618 --> 00:19:02.023
MARAVYANKA, dos iz geven oykhet

00:19:02.023 --> 00:19:06.375
ibern Nemen, aribergeyn dem brik, un dortn iz geven dos oyf rekhts

00:19:06.375 --> 00:19:08.564
iz geven aza dorf

00:19:08.564 --> 00:19:13.104
un oykhet m'hot UNK ⟨untergenumen⟩ fun di felder.

00:19:13.104 --> 00:19:15.293
hot men gearbet.

00:19:15.293 --> 00:19:18.252
mayn shvester hot gekent dem brigadir.

00:19:18.252 --> 00:19:22.131
hot zi gebetn az er zol mir mitnemen.

00:19:22.131 --> 00:19:24.523
hot er mir mitgenumen eyn mol

00:19:24.523 --> 00:19:26.550
un az dernokh dortn

00:19:26.550 --> 00:19:29.901
iz geven, iz dos geven a darzhenik.

00:19:29.901 --> 00:19:31.576
a darzhenik iz

00:19:31.576 --> 00:19:34.859
vos er git akhtung oyf di felder.

00:19:34.859 --> 00:19:38.049
hob ikh bay im gezesn, ikh hob, fleg im neyen

00:19:38.049 --> 00:19:40.846
⟨altsikeding⟩ hob ikh gekent, alts hob ikh gekent neyen.

00:19:40.846 --> 00:19:42.049
hentshkes un

00:19:42.049 --> 00:19:44.089
vos hob ikh nit gekent neyen

00:19:44.089 --> 00:19:46.089
hob ikh far im geneyt.

00:19:46.089 --> 00:19:51.926
dortn ⟨fleg ikh krign⟩ flegt er mir gebn opesn, a teler zup, ikh veys vos opesn

00:19:51.926 --> 00:19:54.169
un mir iz geven gut.

00:19:54.169 --> 00:19:57.805
un m- un yedn frimorgn, az me flegt geyn tsu der arbet

00:19:57.805 --> 00:19:59.588
flegt zogn der brigadir

00:19:59.588 --> 00:20:02.088
"ot dos iz di shnayderke."

00:20:02.088 --> 00:20:04.426
ye. un ⟨mir⟩ flegt men durkhlozn.

00:20:04.426 --> 00:20:06.399
eyn mol

00:20:06.399 --> 00:20:12.020
zits ikh azo- ikh bin dortn bayn, bayn darzhenik, bay dem poyer

00:20:12.020 --> 00:20:14.682
un s'iz gezesn eyner

00:20:14.682 --> 00:20:17.587
eyner a hoykher aza, er hot zikh oysgetsoygn

00:20:17.587 --> 00:20:21.236
azoy vi er iz der oysderveylter.

00:20:21.236 --> 00:20:22.804
ikh hob nit gevust

00:20:22.804 --> 00:20:26.236
az dos iz geven, s'iz geven a politsist Margoles

00:20:26.236 --> 00:20:30.695
un er iz geven bayn toyer. bayn toyer zaynen zey geven

00:20:30.695 --> 00:20:33.424
zogn dem emes, hint.

00:20:33.424 --> 00:20:36.614
nit keyn,

00:20:36.614 --> 00:20:40.614
in, in UNK ⟨rufn⟩ mentshn.

00:20:40.614 --> 00:20:43.479
vemen zey hobn gevelt hobn zey durkhgelozn.

00:20:43.479 --> 00:20:45.370
vemen zey hobn gevelt hot men

00:20:45.370 --> 00:20:49.370
alemen batapt, aroysgeshlept f- un flegt vos oysbaytn.

00:20:49.370 --> 00:20:52.775
flegn kumen bayn toyer, un me flegt ⟨dos⟩ tsunemen fun dir.

00:20:52.775 --> 00:20:57.815
batapn dem boykh, "vos hostu do? vos hostu do?" un tsunemen

00:20:57.815 --> 00:21:00.991
iz er, dos iz geven di Margoles'es

00:21:00.991 --> 00:21:02.275
az, a bruder.

00:21:02.275 --> 00:21:04.964
un ikh hob nit gevust az er iz a bruder.

00:21:04.964 --> 00:21:07.450
un az Margoles ⟨iz⟩ a politsist

00:21:07.450 --> 00:21:13.693
zaynen di brider oykh geven gantse balebatim bayn toyer durkhtsulozn di arbeter.

00:21:13.693 --> 00:21:19.179
zog ikh tsu im azoy, zog azoy "Meyer Margoles, er iz a politsist

00:21:19.179 --> 00:21:22.364
er, zey s- zaynen arbeter, dos"

00:21:22.364 --> 00:21:26.445
ober vos hobn an, a deye di brider

00:21:26.445 --> 00:21:28.702
tsu zogn az UNK bayn toyer?

00:21:28.702 --> 00:21:30.457
mer nit.

00:21:30.457 --> 00:21:34.228
oyfn morgn zogt der brigadir "dos iz di shnayderke."

00:21:34.228 --> 00:21:36.741
zogt er azoy "⟨ha⟩ di shnayderke!

00:21:36.741 --> 00:21:39.268
ir darfn mir take hobn!"

00:21:39.268 --> 00:21:44.052
az er git mir a shlep; ikh bin gegangen in a mantl, do farn kark.

00:21:44.052 --> 00:21:46.809
"di shnayderke," ⟨shlept⟩ mir aroys

00:21:46.809 --> 00:21:48.862
un shlept mir arayn

00:21:48.862 --> 00:21:50.727
dos iz geven antkegn

00:21:50.727 --> 00:21:52.808
dos hot geheysn a DABOKLE.

00:21:52.808 --> 00:21:55.997
a DABOKLE iz dos oyf litvish, dos iz aza min

00:21:55.997 --> 00:21:58.240
turmetshke, ye.

00:21:58.240 --> 00:22:02.511
kh'hob geh- un, un ikh hob shoyn nit gekent fo- geyn oyf

00:22:02.511 --> 00:22:04.551
oyf di un di brigade

00:22:04.551 --> 00:22:09.199
⟨hot⟩ gehaltn mir efsher a dray sho un mir aroysgelozn.

00:22:09.199 --> 00:22:11.442
far vos? far ven?

00:22:11.442 --> 00:22:14.564
vos hob ikh dir geton? vos hob ikh dir gezogt?

00:22:14.564 --> 00:22:15.996
kh'hob zey gezogt az

00:22:15.996 --> 00:22:18.591
az, er iz a politsist

00:22:18.591 --> 00:22:19.969
hot er rekht

00:22:19.969 --> 00:22:22.185
tsu, tsu reydn bayn toyer.

00:22:22.185 --> 00:22:26.135
ober du, di brider, vos far a shaykhes hobn di brider bayn toyer?

00:22:26.135 --> 00:22:28.445
vos hob ikh azoy z- gezogt?

00:22:28.445 --> 00:22:33.147
vayl mir dortn in MARAVYANKA geven gut. ikh fleg neyen a gantsn tog

00:22:33.147 --> 00:22:36.526
un in ovnt flegt men arunternemen mern.

00:22:36.526 --> 00:22:38.363
fleg ikh aroyfgeyn oyfn feld

00:22:38.363 --> 00:22:41.404
fleg zikh onshitn a gantsn rukzak mit mern

00:22:41.404 --> 00:22:46.242
un ikh fleg brengen in sh-, far di, in shtub far di shvester.

00:22:46.242 --> 00:22:50.052
UNK fleg ikh vos efsher oysbaytn oykhet, ye.

00:22:50.052 --> 00:22:57.823
iz mir geven dortn gut, un ikh fleg krign opesn, un ikh fleg ⟨zitsn⟩, un oyfn feld bin ikh nit gegangen; ikh bin gezesn; ikh hob geneyt far im.

00:22:57.823 --> 00:23:01.187
nu, hob ikh shoyn dortn nit gekent geyn.

00:23:01.187 --> 00:23:05.809
dortn nit gekent geyn, hot men genumen

00:23:05.809 --> 00:23:09.741
oyf, in MAISTAS; MAISTAS iz

00:23:09.741 --> 00:23:14.822
vos fun fleysh men makht alerley

00:23:14.822 --> 00:23:17.862
produktn.

00:23:17.862 --> 00:23:21.268
m'hot mir genumen tsu flikn hiner.

00:23:21.268 --> 00:23:24.727
m'hot genumen a g- sakh, a brigade

00:23:24.727 --> 00:23:27.429
tsu MAISTAS tsu flikn hiner.

00:23:27.429 --> 00:23:29.713
un ikh bin oykh arayngefaln.

00:23:29.713 --> 00:23:31.767
flikn di hiner

00:23:31.767 --> 00:23:34.118
iz geven zeyer shver.

00:23:34.118 --> 00:23:37.375
ershtns di fl- hiner hobn azelkhene vos baysn.

00:23:37.375 --> 00:23:39.105
ye? zey krikhn arayn in

00:23:39.105 --> 00:23:41.740
bay di mentshn un zey UNK bayst.

00:23:41.740 --> 00:23:45.198
hob ikh zikh ongeton zeyer laykht untn.

00:23:45.198 --> 00:23:48.698
vayl ikh fleg kumen in shtub, fleg ikh zikh iberton.

00:23:48.698 --> 00:23:50.563
un

00:23:50.563 --> 00:23:55.104
un ikh bin gega- oyfgeshtanen in der fri, un ikh bin gegangen tsu geyn

00:23:55.104 --> 00:23:57.725
in di brigade.

00:23:57.725 --> 00:24:01.563
PITOM, mit a mol, gekumen a politsist

00:24:01.563 --> 00:24:03.576
mit a liste

00:24:03.576 --> 00:24:05.927
er nemt mayn shvester.

00:24:05.927 --> 00:24:09.549
er nemt di shvester mit di kinder, ⟨m'hot gezogt⟩ zogt er

00:24:09.549 --> 00:24:12.968
"ir ⟨vet zayn⟩" zogt er "in a tsveytn ort

00:24:12.968 --> 00:24:15.373
dortn vet ir ale zayn tsuzamen

00:24:15.373 --> 00:24:18.603
un ir vet geyn oyf der arbet."

00:24:18.603 --> 00:24:22.589
un i- un ikh bin nit geven oyf di liste.

00:24:22.589 --> 00:24:25.494
az di shvester, hot men tsugenumen di shvester

00:24:25.494 --> 00:24:27.656
hob ikh ongehoybn veynen

00:24:27.656 --> 00:24:30.562
azoy vi gantse yorn leb ikh mit mayn shvester

00:24:30.562 --> 00:24:34.629
un mit di kinder, mit alemen, ikh zol blaybn eyner aleyn

00:24:34.629 --> 00:24:36.418
hob ikh ongehoybn veynen

00:24:36.418 --> 00:24:38.675
zogt tsu mir der politsist, zogt er

00:24:38.675 --> 00:24:41.648
"vi?" zogt er, "for oykhet ⟨mit⟩" zogt er.

00:24:41.648 --> 00:24:43.932
"vet ir zayn ale tsuzamen."

00:24:43.932 --> 00:24:45.810
zog ikh "gut" zog ikh.

00:24:45.810 --> 00:24:48.133
"vu ir vet zayn dortn vel ikh zayn.

00:24:48.133 --> 00:24:52.977
ale mol zaynen mir tsuzamen, un mir veln ⟨dort⟩ vayter zayn bey- oyf beyde tsuzamen."

00:24:52.977 --> 00:24:58.890
mir hobn gelebt, di shvester hot gelebt oyf a tsveytn etazh, aza bloke geven, oyfn tsveytn etazh.

00:24:58.890 --> 00:25:01.674
ikh bin nokh oyfgelofn in der heykh.

00:25:01.674 --> 00:25:04.998
ikh hob zikh ayngepakt dem tshemodan

00:25:04.998 --> 00:25:06.580
un

00:25:06.580 --> 00:25:09.268
es iz geven groyse GRUZOVIKes

00:25:09.268 --> 00:25:11.511
un ikh bin geforn mit z- mit di

00:25:11.511 --> 00:25:17.290
kinder, ⟨zog ikh⟩ "vu ir vet zayn UNK dortn, vel ikh zayn, un mir ⟨veln⟩ vider zayn ale tsuzamen."

00:25:17.290 --> 00:25:20.158
mir zaynen gekumen tsu forn; m'hot undz gefirt

00:25:20.158 --> 00:25:25.633
mir zaynen arumgeforn oyf a bar- oyfn barg dortn, vu ⟨der⟩ erodrom iz in der hoykh oyfn barg.

00:25:25.633 --> 00:25:30.091
mir zaynen aroyf oyfn barg.

00:25:30.091 --> 00:25:34.862
nit tsu dertseyln.

00:25:34.862 --> 00:25:41.753
vos dortn iz geven.

00:25:41.753 --> 00:25:47.320
in mayn lebn vel ikh dos nit fargesn.

00:25:47.320 --> 00:25:50.334
dortn iz azoy geven:

00:25:50.334 --> 00:25:52.266
mir gibn a kuk.

00:25:52.266 --> 00:25:54.212
mener bazunder

00:25:54.212 --> 00:25:56.077
froyen bazunder

00:25:56.077 --> 00:25:58.185
kinder vider bazunder.

00:25:58.185 --> 00:26:00.496
di kinder shrayen un veynen.

00:26:00.496 --> 00:26:07.688
mayn sh- di meydele iz geven zibn yor iz zi geven, ober zi iz geven a kleyninke, a magerinke aza.

00:26:07.688 --> 00:26:11.242
hot zi arumgekhapt di shvester, un zi shrayt "maminke!

00:26:11.242 --> 00:26:15.660
gib mir nit avek!"

00:26:15.660 --> 00:26:17.769
tsu ir UNK der daytsh

00:26:17.769 --> 00:26:20.390
zi ⟨gegebn⟩ a drey di shvester far di hent.

00:26:20.390 --> 00:26:21.498
zogt er tsu ir

00:26:21.498 --> 00:26:23.350
"DU DUMME FRAU" zogt er.

00:26:23.350 --> 00:26:28.039
"di kinder kenen nit forn mit di, mit di, mit di eltern tsuzamen.

00:26:28.039 --> 00:26:31.755
di kinder veln forn in letstn vagon

00:26:31.755 --> 00:26:36.105
un di eltere froyen veln akhtung gebn oyf di kinder."

00:26:36.105 --> 00:26:38.241
tsugenumen di meydele

00:26:38.241 --> 00:26:41.065
opgeshtelt ikh mit di shvester in eyn zayt

00:26:41.065 --> 00:26:45.011
dem shvoger. mir gebn a kuk az dem yingl tshepet men nit.

00:26:45.011 --> 00:26:47.551
az der yingl iz geblibn lebn shvoger.

00:26:47.551 --> 00:26:51.605
er iz geblibn lebn shvoger mit di, tsulib, veg-

00:26:51.605 --> 00:26:53.091
tsu di mener

00:26:53.091 --> 00:26:56.767
un mir zaynen geblibn tsu di froyen.

00:26:56.767 --> 00:26:59.699
un, un m'hot di kinder tsugenumen

00:26:59.699 --> 00:27:02.388
⟨hot men⟩ tsugenumen ale tshemodanes.

00:27:02.388 --> 00:27:05.429
⟨ az⟩ tshemodanes iz geven a barg biz oybn

00:27:05.429 --> 00:27:07.537
dz- ongevorfn mit tshemodanes.

00:27:07.537 --> 00:27:11.824
m'hot tsugenumen mayn tshemodan. ikh bin geblibn a nakete.

00:27:11.824 --> 00:27:19.323
UNK ikh nor gegangen in mantl, ober untn bin ikh geven nit ongeton varem, vayl ikh bin gegangen in MAISTAS.

00:27:19.323 --> 00:27:23.850
⟨m'iz⟩ gekumen; m'hot undz arayngefirt adernokh in, in a vagon.

00:27:23.850 --> 00:27:28.282
der vagon iz geven a, nu, fun skhoyre, UNK

00:27:28.282 --> 00:27:32.215
un ni- a- posheter vagon azoy.

00:27:32.215 --> 00:27:34.795
UNK arayngeshlept ale vayber

00:27:34.795 --> 00:27:39.119
shoyn vayber bazunder, froyen bazunder, mener bazunder

00:27:39.119 --> 00:27:41.998
un UNK in dem, in vagon

00:27:41.998 --> 00:27:44.565
oyf der erd zaynen mir gezesn

00:27:44.565 --> 00:27:47.592
ye, un me fort.

00:27:47.592 --> 00:27:48.876
m'iz geforn

00:27:48.876 --> 00:27:52.551
un di vagon in der heykh iz geven a kleyninker fentsterl

00:27:52.551 --> 00:27:54.578
fartsoymt mit drotn

00:27:54.578 --> 00:28:00.281
un fun, flegt men, mer nit iz geven keyn likht, nor dos.

00:28:00.281 --> 00:28:02.200
un m'iz geforn

00:28:02.200 --> 00:28:06.619
PITOM hot zikh opgeshtelt der, der,

00:28:06.619 --> 00:28:11.864
der ban hot zikh ave- ge- geblibn shteyn; mir gibn a kuk az me fort nit.

00:28:11.864 --> 00:28:16.269
di hekhere ver hobn a kuk geton, zogn azoy "oy, ⟨ot⟩ iz a vald.

00:28:16.269 --> 00:28:19.242
m'vet undz bald araynfirn in vald un me shist undz oys."

00:28:19.242 --> 00:28:23.458
ye. m- sh- "in vald vet men undz araynfirn un me shist undz oys."

00:28:23.458 --> 00:28:27.080
geshtanen, un mir forn nokh vayter. iz men geforn

00:28:27.080 --> 00:28:31.134
vi lang mir zaynen geforn, vifl teg mir zaynen geforn

00:28:31.134 --> 00:28:33.700
ikh gedenk nit.

00:28:33.700 --> 00:28:36.633
mir zaynen gekumen tsu forn

00:28:36.633 --> 00:28:39.214
gor shoyn in an ander ort

00:28:39.214 --> 00:28:44.781
m'hot undz alemen aroysgenumen; mir gibn a kuk, un mir hobn gemeynt az me geyt dortn undz umbrengen.

00:28:44.781 --> 00:28:46.538
dos iz di ershte zakh.

00:28:46.538 --> 00:28:50.646
mir hobn gemeynt az me geyt undz umbrengen; UNK derbay geven a vald

00:28:50.646 --> 00:28:55.943
mir hobn gemeynt ⟨undz⟩ araynfirn in vald un me shist undz alemen oys.

00:28:55.943 --> 00:28:58.740
m'iz, mir gibn a kuk epes fremde

00:28:58.740 --> 00:29:00.537
penemer, fremde

00:29:00.537 --> 00:29:02.321
 hiters.

00:29:02.321 --> 00:29:04.956
iz dos shoyn geven ESTONTSes.

00:29:04.956 --> 00:29:06.335
zey hobn oykhet

00:29:06.335 --> 00:29:09.726
ge- zey hobn dokh oykh gedint di daytshn

00:29:09.726 --> 00:29:13.036
di ESTONTSes

00:29:13.036 --> 00:29:16.266
un

00:29:16.266 --> 00:29:19.888
un mir zaynen dortn geven

00:29:19.888 --> 00:29:24.388
un m'hot ongehoybn shoyn oyssortirn, mener bazunder, vayber bazunder.

00:29:24.388 --> 00:29:26.726
do ahin, do aher.

00:29:26.726 --> 00:29:31.999
un m'hot arayngeleygt in, oykhet in mashi- GRUZOVIKes, un m'hot undz gebrakht

00:29:31.999 --> 00:29:34.796
tsu firn, ⟨m'hot undz⟩ gebrakht tsu firn

00:29:34.796 --> 00:29:38.161
in a lager vos hot geheysn EREDA.
